  	<item>
  		<title>Skip song from notification popup</title>
  		<p>
  			Right mouse click on the popup, it will show you playback control.
  		</p>
  	</item>
  	<item>
		<title>Start GMPC hidden</title>
  		<p>
  			Start GMPC with: <cmd>gmpc --start-hidden</cmd>
  		</p>
  	</item>
  	  	<item>
		<title>Always start GMPC hidden</title>
  		<p>
  			Edit the GMPC config file: <code>~/.config/gmpc/gmpc.cfg</code>
  			And set:
  		</p>
  			<code mime="text/ini">[Default]
start-hidden="1"
  		</code>
  		<p>
  			Next time you start GMPC it be hidden
  		</p>
  	</item>
  	<item>
  		<title>Change the MPD polling frequency</title>
  		<p>
  			By default GMPC polls MPD for updates every 500 ms (twice a second).
	  		If you are on a slow or high latency connection you might want to
	  		reduce this.
	  		Edit the GMPC config file: <code>~/.config/gmpc/gmpc.cfg</code>
  			And set:
  		</p>
  		<code mime="text/ini">[connection]
mpd-update-speed="1000"
		</code>
		<p>
			to poll every second
		</p>
  	</item>
  </list>
